<h1>Password Reset</h1>

<p>Hey there <%= @user.name %>,</p>
<p>To reset your password, click the link below:</p>
<%= link_to "Reset Password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token,
                                                      email: @user.email) %>
<p>This link will expire in two hours. If you did not request your password to be reset, please disregard this email.</p>
<p>Please do not reply to this notifcation, this inbox is not monitored.</p>
<p>If you are having a problem with your account, please email <%= mail_to "contact@ribbit.com" %></p>